{The bidding has been as shown.   

You don't have a great hand but you <b>DO</b> have 4 \Ss. So don't let the opponents have a 3-level contract when your side has 9 \Ss. Bid 3\S.

Note: See the Law of Total Tricks Lesson on this topic.}

